cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY 

The paper focuses on a vision-based tactile sensor and proposes a strategy to train a deep neural network entirely from simulation data. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) and Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of deep neural networks for learning indicates that the paper may also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the focus on generalization capabilities and transferability across multiple tactile sensors suggests that the paper may also belong to the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category.
